| eng = (''Sa-u-di-a-ra-bi-a'') [[w:Saudi Arabia|Saudi Arabia]]}}
{{Korean/Question-answer | kor= [[wikt:불가리아|불가리아]]            | hint = country in Southeastern Europe
| eng = (''Bul-ga-ri-a'') [[w:Bulgaria|Bulgaria]]}}
{{Korean/Question-answer | kor= [[wikt:루마니아|루마니아]]            | hint = another country in Eastern Europe
| eng = (''Ru-ma-ni-a'') [[w:Romania|Romania]]}}
