| eng = ''Sam-seong'' -> [[w:Samsung|Samsung]]}}
{{Korean/Question-answer | kor = [[wikt:러시아|러시아]] | hint=a country in Northern Asia
| eng = ''Reo-si-a'' -> [[w:Russia|Russia]]}}

