{{Korean/Question-answer | kor = [[wikt:게임|게임]]
| eng = ''ge-im'' -> game}}
{{Korean/Question-answer | kor = [[wikt:메인|메인]]           | hint= the most northeastern US state
| eng = ''Me-in'' -> [[w:Maine|Maine]]}}
{{Korean/Question-answer | kor = [[wikt:말레이시아|말레이시아]] | hint= a country in Southeastern Asia
| eng = ''Mal-le-i-si-a'' -> [[w:Malaysia|Malaysia]]}}
{{Korean/Question-answer | kor = [[wikt:세네갈|세네갈]]       | hint= a country in North Africa
| eng = ''Se-ne-gal'' -> [[w:Senegal|Senegal]]}}
